apons DPS are not good enough for groups and trials in planes. Here is my magelo:<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html">www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
num=485893<br>
<br>
can you guys please give me good advice on what weapons I should upgrade to and what armor I should upgrade to so I can get up to the DPS, AC, and HP that a 61 MA should have. I beg for your expert advice since Im having a hard time seeing how people are hittin 4k hp and 1500ac unbuffed.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gedes>Gedes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/02 7:25:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Asking help from the pros.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=485893" target="top">www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=485893</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Fixed your link for ya..<br>
<br>
<br>
Look down, that is a damn good post right there. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2372"> Thor Lost Myrmidon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/c_warrior.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;It's never too late to be what you might have been - George Eliot&quot;<br>
<br>
</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gedes>Gedes</A> at: 12/19/02 8:15:46 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=celebryn>Celebryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/02 7:59:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Asking help from the pros.</span><hr size=1> Just looking at your Magelo the first thing that struck me was that you have about 3k hps which isnt heaps for a 61 warrior.<br>
<br>
Heres a few upgrades you could look at getting to start with:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=5738" target="top">Bracer of Benevolence</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - 8sta 30hps and not too hard to get.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7424" target="top">Clattering Bone Necklace</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - 6sta 30hps for the neck slot.  Dragon tooth choker is another alternative tho not quite as good.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=4023" target="top">Idol of the thorned</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - good Sta and AC in the range slot.<br>
<br>
For Earrings I would try to get any of the following:<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=12456" target="top">Earring of the Solstice</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=10381" target="top">Spiderfang Earring</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7147" target="top">VahShir Claw Earring</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Or if you've got cash to burn go for the much nicer<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=10375" target="top">Mozzie Earring</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=12702" target="top">Lizard Tooth Earring</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=3998" target="top">Cloak of the Maestrom</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - 6sta 55hps is kinda nice for a back item<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2192" target="top">Hierophant's cloak</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> is another nice alternative<br>
<br>
You don't have any AA's listed in your magelo, so if you dont have them already ND3 is another nice way to get your HPs up a bit.<br>
<br>
The other thing Trial groups will be after when they look for a tank is one who can dish out some decent DPS.  Frosty is a good start, but I dont know how good the ornate sword of the general is gonna be and it might make a difference having the lower delay weapon in primary.  If you have the cash tho, nothing beats a windblade for bang for buck at the moment.<br>
<br>
Just some ideas anyway, hope it helps. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:x-small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=50585">Eoden</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;">Half Elven Warlord<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub142.ezboard.com/bsouthernlegion">Southern Legion</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg">The Tribunal</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=y0shimitzu>y0shimitzu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/02 10:07:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   trial groups </span><hr size=1> don't fell bad... I get thrown out for trial groups all day...  and  I have fairly ok gear...   the trials are all about DPS...  you just need a find a group of SK's and a cleric...   if SK's are using their spells it is a easy trial...   make sure that you guys get rods before the fight though.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=477982">www.magelo.com/eq_view_pr...num=477982</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thehawnz>the hawnz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://images.fotki.com/v13/photos/4/41603/158712/noble-vi.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 162<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/21/02 2:51:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: trial groups </span><hr size=1> i dont know if those stats are right in your profile (i know the ac/attk are wrong obviously..you need to go fill in your defensive and offensive skills in the skills section), but 117 sta sucks.  that right there is making you miss about 500 extra HP you should have.  2nd, get ND3.  that's another ~400 HP.  you definitely need some new earrings.  <br>
<br>
throw away your cougar claws and get solstice earring and a hammered golden hoop (you can camp the latter).<br>
<br>
get some crustacean legs till your sta gets around 200+ unbuffed.  <br>
<br>
get a new mainhand wep.  level 61 warrior with mainhand frosty is eww.  go group in CT and get a fleshgrinder or save up for one or buy a swiftblade of zek (they're getting pretty cheap lately).<br>
<br>
basically, you need to think like this:<br>
<br>
ac till 1200ish<br>
sta till 200+<br>
+HP<br>
<br>
looking for items with all 3 of the above is highly suggested and i would not advise buying much of anything that doesn't have at least sta/hp on it.  get in a raiding guild and start farming tov for ss armor (90hp gloves..common drop).  <br>
<br>
once you get around 4500+ unbuffed HP with better wep, then worry about doing exe trial. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=swoloreslaughterhouse>Swolore Slaughterhouse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/22/02 1:43:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: trial groups</span><hr size=1> Heh by the time I am able to get that much cash I just better quit playing eq.I didnt buy PoP to have to wait 2 more years so I can get into the other tiers. I cant figure out how you guys make so much dang pp all the time to be able to afford to buy these items. Ive only had about 10k max at any moment and that was when I bought my frosty. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=haass>Haass</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 771<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/22/02 4:08:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: trial groups</span><hr size=1> It's all about the attitude you have.  You have the attitude that you want to level, level, level so you can get to the other tier planes.  Other people place their gear at a higher priority level.  For those of us that make sure our gear is the best it can be as we go, we may level a tad slower, but we've got a massive edge over the quick level types.  Look at my profile, i'm 61, and obviously I have the deity advantage, but i have over 1500hp on you.  Are you going to be able to cut it in POV and POS with 3khp?  Probably not, so it's time to sit down and work on the gear.  If that means you gotta get yourself a group in seb and farm up gems for a month to do it, then so be it.  Take care of your equipment and it takes care of you. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48986">Marshall Haass Wolvesbane</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71943">Venerable Cagna Soulshaker</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=4694.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=4694.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4694.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=4694.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=4694.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4694.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4694.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteelwarriorthebunker">The Bunker<option value="thesteelwarriorthetavern">The Tavern<option value="thesteelwarriorfrm6">The Keep<